ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR DATA USAGE:

1. DATA SOURCE ATTRIBUTION
   This software uses data from the Government of India's Open Data Platform 
   (data.gov.in). Users of this software must comply with data.gov.in's terms 
   of service and provide appropriate attribution when using or redistributing 
   the data.

2. GOVERNMENT DATA DISCLAIMER
   The MGNREGA data displayed in this application is sourced from data.gov.in 
   and is subject to the terms and conditions of the Government of India. The 
   authors and contributors of this software are not responsible for the 
   accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of the government data.

3. NO OFFICIAL ENDORSEMENT
   This software is an independent project and is not officially endorsed by, 
   affiliated with, or sponsored by the Ministry of Rural Development, 
   Government of India, or any other government entity.

4. GEOGRAPHIC DATA
   Reverse geocoding services are provided by OpenStreetMap Nominatim. Users 
   must comply with OpenStreetMap's Nominatim Usage Policy available at:
   https://operations.osmfoundation.org/policies/nominatim/

5. THIRD-PARTY SERVICES
   This software integrates with third-party services (data.gov.in, 
   OpenStreetMap). Users are responsible for complying with the terms of 
   service of these platforms.

6. PRIVACY & DATA COLLECTION
   - This software uses browser geolocation with user permission
   - Location data is processed server-side for district detection only
   - No personal data is stored or transmitted to third parties
   - Users should review the privacy policy if deploying this software publicly

7. ACCESSIBILITY COMMITMENT
   This software aims to comply with WCAG 2.1 Level AA accessibility standards. 
   If you encounter accessibility issues, please report them via GitHub Issues.

